provisions.content:
In this Act, unless there is anything repugnant in the subject or context,—
(a)   “Commission” means the Pakistan Banking and Finance Services Commission
established under section 3;
(b) “financial institution” means an institution referred to in the Schedule;
(c) “Member” means a member of the Commission;
(d) “recruitment” means initial appointment otherwise than by promotion or transfer;
(e) “rules” means rules made under section 14; and
(f) “schedule” means the schedule to this Act.
